      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this absolute stunner. It\u2019s been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like a total dream. I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be over the moon. Come swing by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself why this gem is so special\u2014I'm happy to answer any questions you have!",
