    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, ensuring mechanical longevity and peak variable valve timing performance. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory M-variable differential lock. The chassis retains its structural integrity with zero torsional fatigue, and the suspension maintains factory-spec damping rates for optimal lateral grip. Finished in Carbon Black, the exterior exhibits flawless paint depth and perfect panel gaps, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple with no bolster wear. A turn-key, high-revving masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 44500.0,
