      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the term 'mint condition.' This car has been meticulously garaged since day one, protected from the elements and preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory-fresh luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather remains supple and matte, free from any bolster wear or creasing, and still carries that distinctive new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assistance features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians using only OEM parts. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road debris or oxidation. Included are both original keys, the full suite of owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom-fit car cover. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a showroom-quality example that drives as perfectly as it looks.",
